# Speedo - Trip Analytics Dashboard

## Overview

Speedo is a full-stack trip analytics platform that processes GPS trip CSV files and visualizes:

* Route tracking
* Overspeed detection
* Idle duration
* Stoppage duration
* Segment-based analytics
* Interactive map visualization

The project is built using Clean Architecture principles in the backend and a modular feature-based frontend architecture.

---

