# Project Architecture

## Backend Architecture

The backend follows Clean Architecture:

* Domain Layer
* Application Layer
* Infrastructure Layer
* Presentation Layer

## Frontend Architecture

Feature-based modular structure:

* features/
* components/
* hooks/
* services/
* types/
* validations/

