# Environment Variables

## Backend (.env)

```env
PORT=5000
MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_connection_string
JWT_SECRET=your_secret
CLIENT_URL=http://localhost:5173
```

## Frontend (.env)

```env
VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:5000/api
```

